S-Kubric's holders are the Stewards (Educators) , Sentinels (Actuators) and Shields (Evaluators) of the Athena Protocol.

Distribute them wisely keeping in mind that those you choose will be the first to join the Athena Protocol in decentralizing environmental and social governance.
